oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry Duke of Paducah Show at the Porter County Fair
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Split Fountain Printing; Smith, Carl, 1927-2010; Duke of Paducah, 1901-1986; Childre, Lew, 1901-1961; Annie Lou and Danny;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (red and black on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry Duke of Paducah Show with Carl Smith, the Tunesmiths, Annie Lou and Danny, Lew Childre and others at the Porter County Fair on August 5. Poster features metal photoplates of the Duke of Paducah, Carl Smith, the Tunesmiths, Annie Lou and Danny, and Lew Childre.
